{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be playful and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Playful EdTech</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #ff4500; /* Red-Orange for a playful feel */\n            --secondary-color: #ffddcc; /* A lighter, softer shade of red */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #ffa07a; /* Light Salmon for accents */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 1.5rem 1rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            text-align: center;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        p {\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .feature-card {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            width: 28%;\n            min-width: 250px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 3px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .feature-card h3 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 1rem 2rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 1rem;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Simple playful animations for icons/elements if needed */\n        .icon {\n            display: inline-block;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            animation: bounce 1.5s infinite;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        @keyframes bounce {\n            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n            40% {\n                transform: translateY(-15px);\n            }\n            60% {\n                transform: translateY(-10px);\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>SparkLearn</h1>\n        <p>Ignite your curiosity!</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Unlock Your Potential with Fun Learning!</h2>\n        <p>\n            SparkLearn is designed to make education exciting and engaging for everyone.\n            Dive into interactive courses, playful quizzes, and a supportive community\n            that celebrates every step of your learning journey.\n        </p>\n\n        <div class=\"features\">\n            <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                <div class=\"icon\">&#127876;</div>\n                <h3>Interactive Lessons</h3>\n                <p>Learn by doing with hands-on activities and simulations.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                <div class=\"icon\">&#128172;</div>\n                <h3>Gamified Quizzes</h3>\n                <p>Test your knowledge and earn rewards in our fun challenges.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                <div class=\"icon\">&#128100;</div>\n                <h3>Community Support</h3>\n                <p>Connect with learners and mentors worldwide.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Start Learning Today!</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SparkLearn. All rights reserved. Making learning an adventure!</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add more JavaScript for interactive elements if needed\n        // For this example, the animations are CSS-based.\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}